data.description: This charming home, nestled in an established Godard Pary neighborhood with no HOA, offers endless potential. Featuring a spacious layout and classic designs, the main residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2,077 of living space. The original exposed wood beams create a warm and inviting atmosphere while the negotiable fridge, washer and dryer offer ease with your move. One of the standout features of this property is the additional bar/mancave/she shed/kitchen located in the backyard providing the perfect opportunity for fun, cuisine-oriented gatherings. The kitchen is extended by a covered patio while the backyard still offers plenty of green space for play and pets. Take a tour online now and call to see it yourself and OwnYourParadise!
